# Assignments
- Again, write it like a report to your boss
    - no results hanging around without explanation
    - if you show something there should be a reason
    - alternatively, simply saying 'yes' is not enough. 
        - Plots help, so do sentences.
    - be careful with labeling of axes.
    - be careful of losing data 
        - if you start out with 46 rows and end up with 23, you better explain why
    - figure out what you are gong to do about ties and make your sentences and code match
    - if you have a reference for something, please indicate where it was used, eg # ref 1
    - hiding code with echo=false is a bad idea because when you are explaining what went wrong to your boss you won't recall what the hidden code did
- Show **Donor Base Size**

